- A "captain" refers to a driver;
- A "voyage" refers to a trip;
- "Embarked on more than one voyage" means the driver has at least one trip assigned.

sql:
SELECT AVG(trip_duration) AS overall_average_trip_duration
FROM trips
INNER JOIN trip_assignments ON trips.trip_id = trip_assignments.trip_id;

